### Backend (.NET Core)

#### [MODIFY] [DoctorAppointmentSystem.csproj](file:///d:/shivam/doctor-appointment-system/DoctorAppointmentSystem/DoctorAppointmentSystem/DoctorAppointmentSystem.csproj)
- Add package dependency for `Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer`.

#### [MODIFY] [appsettings.json](file:///d:/shivam/doctor-appointment-system/DoctorAppointmentSystem/DoctorAppointmentSystem/appsettings.json)
- Add secure `Jwt` settings: Secret Key, Issuer, and Audience.

#### [MODIFY] [Program.cs](file:///d:/shivam/doctor-appointment-system/DoctorAppointmentSystem/DoctorAppointmentSystem/Program.cs)
- Register Authentication services: `builder.Services.AddAuthentication(JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme).AddJwtBearer(...)`.
- Update the HTTP pipeline to call `app.UseAuthentication()` before `app.UseAuthorization()`.

#### [MODIFY] [AuthService.cs](file:///d:/shivam/doctor-appointment-system/DoctorAppointmentSystem/DoctorAppointmentSystem/Application/Services/AuthService.cs)
