## 3. Verification Plan

### Automated Verification
- Verify that both projects compile cleanly.

### Manual Verification
1. Open the application in the browser at `/patient/dashboard` when logged out. Verify it automatically redirects to `/patient/login`.
2. Register and log in. Verify a secure JWT token is generated and stored.
3. Access dashboard and check request headers in browser Network tab. Confirm `Authorization: Bearer <token>` is present.
4. Manually clear the DB or token from local storage. Confirm that attempting to make any request triggers an immediate logout redirect back to `/login`.
